    Love Story


    We met in Cape Town, through a mutual friend. When I first saw Emmanuel, he felt familiar, as though we’ve met before, although I had no recollection of the encounter. And for Emmanuel, it was love at first conversation because of how passionate Thobeka is when she speaks.

    Our love for nature and exploration science was a hot topic as we were getting to know each other, alongside our faith in God and our passion for the mission. 

    Emmanuel drove from Botswana to take Thobeka out for their first date. He got turned at the gate, because she wasn’t ready. His patience paid off! 
    Even on our first date, we both knew that this was it, that this was the beginning of an incredible journey together, to grow, learn, play and explore.

    Emmanuel proposed at Table Mountain in Cape Town, it was one of the happiest moments of both our lives. Thobeka’s said yes without hesitation, when she could finally speak.
